divs: Sighting Details Theres not a hole lot I can say about this.I found it in a creek.If this is not a real fossilized alien skull then mother nature made one hell of a cool looking rock.I'll just let the picture do the talkin.I have this in my home and want to have it checked for DNA.I've had it a couple of years and would love to find out once and for all if its a real alien skull or just a cool looking rock.My opinion is that it looks to real not to be.I know this sight is for ufo sightings but I thought you might want to check this out.I dont know where else to turn to for asking for help with this.You can have all the samples you need.I'm not opposed to you drlling in to it.
